===Etymology===
{{Han compound|玉|里|c1=s|c2=p|t1=jade|ls=psc}}

The original meaning was "veins in jade". The "logic" meaning might come from the association between jewels on a string and threads of a reasonning process.

According to the [[w:Shuowen_Jiezi|Shuo Wen]], the character meant "to polish jade". The current meaning "to order, tidy up" might come from it.

